<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
	xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd">
	<modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>
	<groupId>net.zamasoft</groupId>
	<artifactId>zs-font</artifactId>
	<packaging>jar</packaging>
	<version>1.2.2</version>
	<name>Font Library</name>
	<description>
Apache Batik 1.7 のフォント読み込みライブラリ(org.apache.batik.svggen.font)から派生したフォントライブラリです。	
TrueType, OpenType(CFF-flavor) の読み込みに対応しています。
	</description>
	<url>https://copper.osdn.jp/zs-font/</url>	
	
	<build>
	    <extensions>
            <extension>
                <groupId>org.apache.maven.wagon</groupId>
                <artifactId>wagon-ssh</artifactId>
                <version>3.0.0</version>
            </extension>
        </extensions>
		<plugins>
			<plugin>
				<artifactId>maven-compiler-plugin</artifactId>
				<version>3.10.1</version>
				<configuration>
					<encoding>UTF-8</encoding>
					<source>1.8</source>
					<target>1.8</target>
					<excludes>
					</excludes>
					<testExcludes>
					</testExcludes>
				</configuration>
			</plugin>
		</plugins>
	</build>
	<reporting>
		<plugins>
			<plugin>
				<groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
				<artifactId>maven-javadoc-plugin</artifactId>
				<configuration>
					<source>1.8</source>
					<encoding>UTF-8</encoding>
					<docencoding>UTF-8</docencoding>
					<charset>UTF-8</charset>
					<links>
						<link>https://docs.oracle.com/javase/jp/8/docs/api/</link>
					</links>
				</configuration>
			</plugin>
		</plugins>
	</reporting>

	<licenses>
		<license>
			<name>Apache 2</name>
			<url>http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.txt</url>
			<distribution>repo</distribution>
			<comments>A business-friendly OSS license</comments>
		</license>
	</licenses>
	<organization>
		<name>座間ソフト</name>
		<url>https//zamasoft.net/</url>
	</organization>
</project>